- In-game Journals<br>
- 160以上の Unique Monster Types<br>
- Advanced Chat, Guild and Grouping System(Factionに基づくchat and grouping optionsあり)<br>
- EQとEQ2に特別なcrossover quest zones, chat system and more!<br>
